		<RichText x="738" y="287" width="435" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">西尼阿斯蓄力发射3枚水球，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%,10%</span><span>伤害，并扣除角色</span><span color="#72ff72">30点</span><span>元素能量，若能量不足则扣除一定比例的生命值，扣除值(A=0.20 B=600 C=30)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="430" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">西尼阿斯生成<span textDecoration="underline">水渊之滨</span><span>，并在自身周围产生吸能场，每0.5s扣除角色</span><span color="#72ff72">10点</span><span>元素能量，能量不足则扣除一定比例的生命值，扣除值(A=0.10 B=100 C=10)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">西尼阿斯后撤，向前翻滚，用尾部扫两圈，造成2段<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="429" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">西尼阿斯连续喷射6枚水球，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%,10%</span><span>伤害，水球效果略有不同，扣除角色</span><span color="#72ff72">20点</span><span>元素能量，扣除值(A=0.15 B=300 C=20)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/西尼阿斯.assets/Image_31.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
