		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">西尼阿斯后撤一步，进行左、右、砸3段攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">40%,60%,100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/西尼阿斯.assets/Image_37.png')" x="720" y="1098">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="67" y="1247" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="343" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值扣除计算公式(传奇专用)</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/西尼阿斯.assets/Image_38.png')" x="64" y="1280" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1164" width="436" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水渊之滨：<span color="#7fbfff">16水</span><span>盾，存在时抗性小幅提升；破除后其将短暂瘫痪，并恢复队伍角色全部元素能量(不含特殊能量)。<br/>特殊能量视为0元素能量，吸能将直接造成扣血，而不吸能量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
